Feature: Create Vouchers

  Background:
    When I go to the Home page

    And I click on the Create Campaign link
    Then the browser is at the Create Campaign page

    When I select "Single Use Transferable" from campaignType
    And I enter a random campaign name
    And I enter the values
      | description      | desc_text           |
      | pomOfferId       | pom_id_sut          |
      | secondaryOfferId | secondaryOfferIdSut |
      | start            | Sat Jan 01 2000 00:00:00 GMT+0000 (BST) |
      | end              | Sun Jan 01 2090 00:00:00 GMT+0000 (BST) |
      | cap              | 100                 |
    And I click the Create Campaign button
    And I wait until the campaign links are displayed
    Then the browser is at the List Campaigns page
    When I click on the campaign we just created

  Scenario: Create Batch of Vouchers
    When I click on the Show Create Vouchers link
    And I enter the values
      | sizeBatch | 100 |

    And I click the Create Voucher Batch button
    And I wait for the voucher batches to display
    Then the text "Creating Voucher Batch" is displayed on the page
    Then I wait for the "History" button to display
    And the table with class "batches" has the following headers with corresponding first row values
      | Vouchers     | 100   |
      | Redeemed     | 0     |
      | Generated By | admin |

  Scenario: Create Single Voucher
    When I click on the Show Create Vouchers link

    And I enter the values
      | caseNumber         | 12345678 |
      | requestedAccountId | 12345678 |

    And I click the Create Voucher button
    And I wait for the voucher batches to display
    Then the text "Created Voucher" is displayed on the page
    Then I wait for the "History" button to display
    And the table with class "batches" has the following headers with corresponding first row values
      | Vouchers     | 1     |
      | Redeemed     | 0     |
      | Generated By | admin |